Commands:

docker pull imagename
docker create CA
docker start CA-ID
docker ps or docker ps -a -q - it shows all CS-ID'S and status
docker rm -f CA-ID -- to delete CA
docker rmi image -- to delete docker image.
docker run -d image -- it directly downlode image and create CA and will start it.

